<div class="ms-3" style="width: 500px;">
  <h1 class="mt-4">Forgot Password</h1>
  <p>Enter your email address below and we'll send you a link to reset your password.(Also check your spam folder if you can't find the mail)</p>

  <form action="/forgot-password" method="POST">
    <label for="email" class="form-label">Email Address:</label>
    <input class="form-control forgot-email-input mb-2" type="email" id="email" name="Email" required >
    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark ">Send Reset Link</button>
  </form>

</div>

